Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:15.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何があったんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:17.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ってか 大丈夫ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:22.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すべて 私のせいなの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:26.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は 私は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:29.74,盛夏-JP上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 皆どこ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:29.72,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:38.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆 どこ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd they all go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:47.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,え 何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:49.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:57.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:00.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:02.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Takatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:07.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,た 貴月先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to Earth on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:09.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:11.92,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この船に乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:14.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この星にやってきました
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:20.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は この星の人間ではありません
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not from this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.16,0:01:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:25.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだ 僕はそのことを知っていたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I already knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.97,0:01:29.61,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから 驚いたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wasn't surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{part a}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is like straight out of a sci-fi movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何っつうか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:43.15,诸神-警示标语-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(629,16)}本字幕由诸神字幕组制作，仅供交流学习，禁止用于商业用途\N更多中日双语字幕，请登录www.kamigami.org
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:43.15,诸神-staff-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,日听：秋水无痕 翻译：yaya 校对：小草爱吃梨 Syura 时间轴：小青
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:36.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ＳＦだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:40.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これ 動かないの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I got into an accident on my way to this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この星に来る途中で事故に遭って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't fly, and the computer system isn't fully functional either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:46.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今は 航行できない状態で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:48.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,システムにも不具合出てて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning on just living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:52.48,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本来なら ここで生活する予定だったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you went to Kirishima's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:55.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それで 霧島君の家に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I had other reasons too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:58.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,他にも理由があるんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that robot thing earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:02.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で さっきのメカメカしいの何です
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it attack you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:04.54,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなた 襲ってきたとか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:06.00,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ち 違うの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was an emergency rescue pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:10.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれは 緊急用の救助ボットで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship automatically sent a distress signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:11.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この船が その
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:14.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,自動的に発信した救難信号をうけて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was trying to rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:17.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私を救助しに来たの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And you broke it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:19.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それ 壊しちゃったんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it just happened that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その 成り行きで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just happened that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:22.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,成り行き
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship is grounded, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.61,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この船は動かないんですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't want to be rescued?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:28.12,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,救助されなくてよかったんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.09,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よくはないんだけど でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to stay on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まだ この星にいたかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:37.00,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:39.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は この星にある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here looking for a certain place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:41.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ある場所を探しに来たの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:42.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ある場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A place in my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:45.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の記憶の中にある場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know if it really exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:49.35,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当にあるかどかも分からないんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:51.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,行ってみたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:53.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから その
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,安心してください 先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't tell anybody you're an alien,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩が宇宙人だなんて 誰にも言ったりしませんから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ま まあな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like anybody would believe us even if we told them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.35,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つうか 先輩が宇宙人だって言ったって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:07.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誰も信じねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the Men in Black found me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.28,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも メン イン ブラックに知られたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:12.66,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't really exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:14.65,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな組織ありませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd dissect me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:16.25,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,か 解剖とか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:17.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,されません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you were worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:19.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなことを心配してたんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.01,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だ だって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Takatsuki, I'll keep it a secret too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:24.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,貴月先輩 私も誰にも言いません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:25.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:27.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誰にも 言いません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:29.22,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:31.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,迷惑かけて ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,謝る必要ないです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:41.62,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの せっかくだから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're here anyway, can I look around a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:43.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここ 見学してていいですか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time, Tetsuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎 こんな時に 何を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a once in a lifetime opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:48.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だって こんなチャンスめったにないぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so, Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.77,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,美桜だって思うだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:52.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まあ そうかもしれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing is fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,確かに 興味深いわね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:55.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:02.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わあ やっぱ すげえな これ 超便利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing {\i1}and{\i0} super convenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:03.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:05.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう こんな時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's gotta be really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:07.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ママたち絶対心配してる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:10.00,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかたねえから 送っててやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:12.14,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で 姉ちゃん 忘れてた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap, I forgot about my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I kept you here so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:13.28,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんな遅い時間まで 引き止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:18.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,話を聞いてもらって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:23.14,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,心配しないで イチカは いつも通りでいればいいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just act like you usually do, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really surprised that Takatsuki's an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:28.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,驚きだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.72,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,貴月先輩が宇宙人だなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I {\i1}still{\i0} can't believe it{'s not butter}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:33.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,っていうか 未だに 信じられない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be more likely to believe it was all just a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:36.63,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どっきりだって言われたほうが信じちゃいそう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I've had suspicions for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:40.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あら 私は薄々感づいていたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like a lie, but I can't say for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:44.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ウソっぽいけど 完全に否定できない感じ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. I know because I'm an agent of the Men in Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:47.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当よ だって私
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,メン イン ブラックのエージェントだもの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now {\i1}that's{\i0} a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それはウソです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of joke is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:52.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,っていうか 何なんです その冗談
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Takatsuki would totally freak out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.49,盛夏-JP上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,貴月先輩 怖がっちゃいます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's Kai gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:56.85,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海のやつ どうするつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a really long day, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:02.32,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんか いろいろあって すごい一日でしたね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:03.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,早く帰って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get home and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:04.32,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I haven't told you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:08.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私 海人君にまだ言ってないことがある
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:09.66,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first came to this planet in my spaceship,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:13.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙船で 初めて この星に来たとき
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I... You were...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:17.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私 海人君に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:17.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,助かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've died back then if it hadn't been for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのとき 先輩がいてくれなかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:24.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺 死んでたかもしれないんですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:27.00,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,知ってたの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:29.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,知っていたというか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,思い出したというか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I used technology from my home planet to heal you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の星の技術で治療したから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:36.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何が問題があるかもしれないと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was worried about possible side effects...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:38.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それで俺んちに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you stayed with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:40.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.22,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ 気にしないでください
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,事故だろうがなんだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was just an accident, but it led me to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それで 先輩に会うことができて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm really glad it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:48.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺 本当に嬉しいんです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah. The problem isn't that she's an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:54.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう 問題なのは 先輩が宇宙人だってことじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:57.35,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなことじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:02.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいのよ 謝らなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually feel better after telling everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆にちゃんと話せてかえってすっきりしたから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the Federation Police finds out that their rescue pod was destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:07.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,けど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,救助ボットを壊されたことを知った連盟保安局が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,they might send somebody to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:13.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,調査員を派遣してくるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That might cause problems for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:17.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうなったら 皆に迷惑がかかるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:20.95,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また 傷つけてしまうかも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might hurt him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,時間は限られてる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have much time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's slowly running out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:26.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,残された時間は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since you came to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,久しぶりだね 美桜がうちに来るの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:34.95,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんね いきなり 泊まりたいなんて言い出して
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for just saying I wanted to stay over all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no problem, but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それはいいんだけど どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I thought you weren't sure what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:42.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜が戸惑ってるだろうなって思って
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Takatsuki just told us she's an alien...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:47.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そりゃね 貴月先輩が宇宙人だなんて聞かされたら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:48.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.48,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,霧島君のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:53.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,霧島君 どうするんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If Takatsuki's an alien, then someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:57.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,貴月先輩が宇宙人だってことは 先輩はいつか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,言わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think about that, I start to hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:05.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それを考えたら 私 すごく嫌な子になる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:06.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずるい子になる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:08.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずるくていいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't help loving someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:10.72,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きは止まらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,止まってくれないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how do you know how I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:18.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,っていうか どうして 私の気持ち知ってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,バレバレでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito! Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:25.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君 今まで 本当にお世話になりました
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.70,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私 実家に帰ります
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget about you and the time we spent together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:31.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君のこと ここで過ごした意味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:34.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,絶対 絶対に忘れないね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get a job or do whatever I have to and come to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩 俺 バイトでも何でもして
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:38.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,必ず会いに行きますから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But my home's in the Andromeda Galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:42.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 私の実家 アンドロメダだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:50.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,２３０万光年か
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 2.3 million light years away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:56.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙って 広いんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Space is big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:07:59.95,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おはよう 海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kaito. I'm going out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私 ちょっと出かけてくるね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:05.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ 出かけるって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もしかして あの場所ってところを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to look for that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I made breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:12.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん 朝食作っておいたから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,夕ご飯までには 帰ってくるね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:20.54,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何してるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Staying on this planet will only make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:23.28,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この星に居続けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆に迷惑かけるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should call for rescue right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.72,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今すぐ救助を呼んだほうがいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why don't I go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして 私 帰らないんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mio... Why don't we stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:37.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 美桜 やっぱり やめとかない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:38.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was just yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:41.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だって 昨日の今日だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:43.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,正確に言うと 今日の今日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I even say to Takatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:46.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな風に 貴月先輩と接していいか 分かんないし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overthink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.60,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,余計なこと 考えないで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just act like you usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,普段通りにすればいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:51.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,考えちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:53.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいから いいから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, has your personality changed since you got your haircut?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:56.62,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,美桜 髪切ってから 性格変わってない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:58.01,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何があった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:08:59.60,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,別に
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:03.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何も ないですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:06.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ 何してんの お前ら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So she's gone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:11.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうか 貴月先輩 出かけてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's out looking for the place she was talking about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.09,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日 言ってた場所を探しに行くって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She went alone? Why would she be so secretive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:17.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一人で行ったんだと 水くさいよな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We would've helped her if she asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:19.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いってくれりゃ 俺らも協力するのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she has a lot on her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:24.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いろいろ考えることがあるんじゃないかな やっぱり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna film something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.63,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,撮影っすか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:27.41,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sidestep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よい あそこ行って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretend to get hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:32.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい 攻撃受けて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I first learned about him from the rumors my classmates shared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:40.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,彼のことを知ったのは クラスメートのうわさ話がきっかけだった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:41.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,転入生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he's the grandson of old man Kirishima at town hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:45.01,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,役場に行った霧島の爺さんの孫だって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the weirdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:46.69,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はあ あの偏屈な
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom said he lost his parents in an accident and came back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,両親が事故で無くなって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:51.09,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こっちに戻ってきたって ママが言ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.62,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ 可哀想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, take a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:55.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆 席に付いて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:10:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce your new classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:59.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日から 皆と一緒に勉強する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,転入生を紹介するわね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:05.86,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(580,317)\blur1\fscx90\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\fnpastel\b0}Kirishima Kaito
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kirishima Kaito from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:03.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,東京から来た 霧島海人です
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よろしくお願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.70,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう言って微笑んだ彼は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When he said that with a smile on his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he didn't look like someone who just lost his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とても 両親を失ったばかりとは思えなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,自分の身になってみると
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I imagine myself in his position, I didn't see myself smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とても 笑える状況じゃないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the way he kept trying to smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:21.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それでも 笑おうとしている彼が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,多分 もう あの時から
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think that's when I started to like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That expression on his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.62,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,意識していたんだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:32.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの時の表情が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just like
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the one he has now.{DEEP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:35.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今の海人君と
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:37.88,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(643,480)\fs70\blur0.55}You
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:37.88,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(711,203)\blur0.55}Episode Nine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:37.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ダブる
