Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can buy more film if I run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フィルムが足りなきゃ売買し
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should take an umbrella too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あとは 一応傘とかも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:49.22,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ おはようございます 先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日は 早いんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to look around again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.77,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日も 探しに行くんですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:58.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺にも 手伝わせてください
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:00.77,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,映画の撮影も皆に頼んで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked the others for a day off from filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:02.51,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しばらく 休みにしましたから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We could...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:03.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これからは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:06.72,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの 私 一人で行くから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君に迷惑をかけられないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to cause any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:12.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これは 私個人の問題だし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:13.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, but I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:17.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:19.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,映画頑張って じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:20.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I said we weren't filming today, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:30.42,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日は 撮影なしだって言ったろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:32.01,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,来ちゃまずいのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not want me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:33.69,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まずくはないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:35.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うまいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:36.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,西瓜じゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika's out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:40.18,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イチカ先輩 また 出かけてんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:44.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで 手伝ってやらねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She said the problem was hers and refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,個人の問題だからって断られた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She wished us luck with with the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.70,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,映画頑張ってってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうか えっ どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered some scenery shots I wanted to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:54.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,撮ってない風景カット思いだした
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.48,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょっと 軽井沢行ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go home, lock the doors here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.27,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,帰るんなら 戸締り頼むな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:00.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょっ 海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the key in the usual spot, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,鍵はいつもんとこでいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:03.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいからって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうするんだよ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:10.97,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:11.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What, more watermelon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:12.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:14.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また西瓜かよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Off to film trees and rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,風景カット撮ってくるってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And Takatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:20.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,貴月先輩は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:22.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,出かけてるって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:25.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それで あんたは何してんの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:26.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:28.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,え 何何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from when we went to Karuizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これ 軽井沢のときの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You look so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛く撮れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Takatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:40.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,貴月先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:43.42,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ええ こんなの撮ってたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know he took this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:52.70,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,え ああ ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何でもない 何でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:56.69,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat some watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.69,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それより 西瓜食べよ 西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{bg}It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:05.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,暑いね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{bg}Yeah! Should we...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛らしい坊やね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go on a date with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私とデートしない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in a million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.65,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,心より遠慮します
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You mad{, bro}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:15.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いらいらしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I {\i1}look{\i0} mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:16.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう見えます
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:17.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet something happened between you and Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうね イチカと何かあったとか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何も ありませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, she won't let me do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:26.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,というか 何もさせてもらえないんです
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:28.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩に俺の気持ちは分かりませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:33.56,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ガキね 自分の思い通りにならないから 不貞腐れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sulking because things aren't going your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:34.97,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうなんじゃないんです
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do you know how Ichika feels?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:38.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ あなたにイチカの気持ちが分かるの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:41.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イチカが何を考えて どう思って
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What went through her mind and how did she feel when she came to this planet alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一人でこの星に来たと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she thinking and feeling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:45.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今何を考え
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:47.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どう思って行動しているか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you thought about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.72,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,霧島君は考えたことがあるのかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After all the courage it must've taken to tell you who she really is, have you done anything for her in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:52.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,勇気を出して
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:55.41,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,自分の正体を打ち上げたイチカに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:57.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたは何か答えてあげた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺は 何をすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you should be thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それを考えなさいと言ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do for her? What {\i1}should{\i0} you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:10.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イチカのために何ができるか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何をしたらいいか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.09,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イチカのことを思っているなら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you care about her, you should find your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:16.92,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,答えは出るはずよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:24.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,考えています
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:28.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう 動くのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:32.41,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらずに 前に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't look back.
