Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Kai doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:48.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海のやつ 何やってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's never home, and he doesn't pick up his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:50.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここのとこ ずっとうちにもいねえし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:52.27,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,電話にも出ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:57.34,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さとしのバカ 帰らないもん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi, you jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:15:00.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つうか いい加減に帰れよ 姉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home already, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人 君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The person I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:20.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の 好きな人は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}love...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.01,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The person I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already been to FT-32, so next is PF...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:32.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ＦＤ３２は調べたから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,次はＢＦ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:42.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どこ行くんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanigawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to look for that place again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また 場所っていうのを探しに行くんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you find it, you're going back to your home planet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で それを見つけたら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:58.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さよならって感じで自分の星に帰って行くんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいですよ 別に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I should consider myself lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:03.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私にとっては ラッキーです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:07.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だって私 海人君が好きですから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,love Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be perfect if one edge of the triangle just disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:12.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ライバルがいなくて へ へへへってもんです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanigawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:14.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川さん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know how Kaito feels about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.56,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩 気づいてるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.27,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君の気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:22.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私が分かっちゃうぐらいなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you should too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.42,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩だって気づいてるはずです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:27.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そして もう一つ気づいてるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You love him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:31.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩も 海人君のことが好きだって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:33.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうなんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な 何言ってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:39.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you not tell him because you're an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:41.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙人だから ダメっていうんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't be with him because you can't stay here forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:46.01,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつまでも一緒にいられないから海人君の気持ちに答えられないっていうんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to use that as an excuse to keep running away from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:48.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういうの言い訳にして
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:51.18,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君からずっと逃げ続ける気ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:55.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,逃げるんだなんて そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're running right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:57.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,現に今そうしています
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.62,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は あの場所を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretending to look as hard as you can for that place so you don't have to face him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,探すことに一生懸命の振りして
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:05.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君から 目を背けてる 逃げてる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:07.14,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だってどうしようもないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私はいつまでも この星に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしようもある
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:10.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell him you love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きだって言えばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you tell him?{and you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.29,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで言わないの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Two people in love can be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:17.96,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きな人と結ばれるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:19.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,素敵なことじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something I can't have no matter how much I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:21.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私がどんなに望んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:23.14,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,手に入らないものが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.96,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すぐそこにあるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こじつけばっかで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet all you do is make excuses and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:27.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,逃げてばっかで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know what Kaito is doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:32.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君が今何をしてるかも知らないくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:38.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君 海人君は 何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:41.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それぐらい 自分で調べよ バッカ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Find out for yourself, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:57.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:02.25,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして あんたがここにいるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you {\i1}like{\i0} seeing me in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:07.27,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,振られた私を見るのがそんなに楽しい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you just pretending to help me so you could see this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:09.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,応援する振りをして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:10.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こうなるのが見たかったわけ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,悪趣味だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:14.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,バカ 行ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:16.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,帰ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:19.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,泣かせてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,頼むよ 柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Kanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:30.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,泣くなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きなの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a tree and a lake...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:01.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,木があって 池があって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what else there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何があるんだろうな そこに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:24.77,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんなもんかな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:26.07,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,次は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:29.85,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,せ 先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:31.63,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, nobody asked you to be so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:35.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう 格好いいことしっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking for it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,探してくれてたんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:40.66,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I shouldn't've...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すみません 勝手なことを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking I had to go home
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:46.22,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私ね 帰らなきゃいけないって思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'd only cause trouble for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:49.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私のせいで 皆に迷惑がかかるから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 帰りたくなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanigawa made me realize that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:57.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川さんが気づかせてくれたの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's not just because I want to find the place in my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:19:59.51,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,帰りたくない理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの場所に行きたいからだけじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:07.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あ あの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you love an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙人でいいですか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:13.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私なんかでいいです
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,May I confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:19.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,告白してもいいですか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:20.60,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:24.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺からします
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:29.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きです ずっと好きでした
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと好きでした
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,From the first time I saw you, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:37.85,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと初めて会ったときから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me a while to understand myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:41.56,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は 分からなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but I fell in love too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:46.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 好きに なってた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:50.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}I looked for the reason why I fell in love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:58.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}and tried solemn words
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:21:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know... that was my first kiss, so, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:58.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの 何っつうか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺 初めてだったから その
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:05.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}Once I realized my feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.51,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は四回目よ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time was at the dam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:05.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一回目はダムで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:13.12,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}the threads had gotten hopelessly tangled up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The second was when you collapsed by the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:08.60,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,二回目は玄関で倒れたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The third was after you were attacked by the rescue pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:12.42,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,三回目は 救助ボットに襲われたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,全部 俺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:17.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}If I'd been able to say it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was to transfer healing nanomachines from my body to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:17.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の中の治療用のマシーンを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:21.12,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}without hesitation{tamerawanaide ieta no nara}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:19.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君に送り込むために
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad they worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うまく合致してくれてよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:26.59,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}you wouldn't have to cry now{kimi wa mou nakanai no}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:23.70,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not romantic at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,全然 ロマンティックじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:27.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:29.35,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まだあるんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:34.27,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}We paint a picture of feelings that pierce the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes my fifth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:32.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これで五回目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:42.77,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}Forever will we remember the scent of summer on the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:46.44,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}My memories of when I was with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:58.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}put color into my life, drop by drop, like the evening rain
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:09.78,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1031,149.667)\blur0.4\c&H0B0C0A&}Episode Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:09.78,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1016.667,380)\fs70\blur0.4\c&H0B0C0A&}Yours and Ours{\b1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:02.79,Default,,0,0,10,,Just as joy exists because of sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:03.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しみがあるから 喜びがあるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:06.40,Default,,0,0,10,,one person's happiness is another's sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:04.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誰かの幸せのかげで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:06.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誰かが涙をこぼす
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:07.86,Default,,0,0,10,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:07.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それが分かっていても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:09.78,Default,,0,0,10,,love knows no obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:09.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,強い思いはたまらない
